What you need to know:

Already, some interns have been absorbed by the organisations they were deployed to after proving their competency.Others applied and were competitively appointed for positions advertised by the Public Service Commission, while others have left to pursue careers in the private sector.For those who will not have found substantive positions at the expiry of the internship period, they will be considered competitively alongside other deserving applicants for any Public Service jobs advertised by the Public Service Commission.